The '''Lonatran Gardens''' was a botanical reserve located on the [[Gree Enclave/Legends|Gree Enclave]] world of [[Lonatro]] and was home to many [[Species/Legends|species]] of rare and exotic plants. The Lonatran Gardens were maintained through [[Gree (species)/Legends|Gree]] genetic manipulations which allowed for species of plants hitherto thought to be extinct to be present on this [[Planet/Legends|world]] and in the Gardens.<ref name="The Gree Enclave">{{JournalCite|8|The Gree Enclave}}</ref>

